### Rakshasa

__Highly intelligent evil spirits that take the form of feline humanoids, with the head of a great cat (e.g. tiger, panther), eerie reversed hands, and cruel claws. Prefer a diet of human flesh. Use their powers of illusion to gain the trust of people, then__
