### Revenant

__The corpse of a person who was murdered, reanimated by the desperate need for revenge. Only the most obsessive individuals return from death in this way.__
[[table style=“border: 0px padding:1px; text-align:left”]]
     [[row]]
     [[cell]]
**Armour Class**
     [[/cell]]
     [[cell]]
9 [10]
     [[/cell]]
     [[/row]]
     [[row]]
     [[cell]]
**Hit Dice**
     [[/cell]]
     [[cell]]
8* (36hp)
     [[/cell]]
     [[/row]]
     [[row]]
     [[cell]]
**Attacks**
     [[/cell]]
     [[cell]]
1 × grasp (2d8 + throttle)
     [[/cell]]
     [[/row]]
     [[row]]
     [[cell]]
**THAC0**
     [[/cell]]
     [[cell]]
12 [+7]
     [[/cell]]
     [[/row]]
